{
  "stem": "8569.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- she-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the-- 'pride' was a middle name, I would say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we were crossing the street in Warsaw and there was a great deal of traffic, she wouldn't look left or right.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She would cross right through, and the traffic had to stop for her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember I used to die a thousand death.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this was the kind of woman she was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We always had help in the house, so I never knew my mother to do any household duties.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And yet, the particular strength of hers came during the war when, after the bombing of Warsaw, we didn't have any electricity and heating or any water.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Ordinarily, the apartment used to be heated by coal in a tile-covered kind of a covered fireplace.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And during the war, my mother, with her own hands, took out the tile from this place and put in a wood-burning stove to heat the apartment.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this was the first time that I have seen my mother doing something manual.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was so completely out of character.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And her strengths came also doing the war when, regardless of the conditions and circumstances, she was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] very particular in the way we looked and dressed.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she used to sole our shoes with leather that was taken from my father's factory transmission belts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she used to sew our clothes and make absolutely sure that we looked the way we are supposed to look, regardless of what was going on around us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's the kind of person she was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was spoiled rotten.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could do anything I wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was really terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It didn't go well with my mother, who was a disciplinarian.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
